videos.headline: Sylvia Fowles glides through lane for and-1 vs. All-Stars
videos.description: Sylvia Fowles gets downhill and finishes through contact for Team USA vs. the WNBA All-Stars.

videos.headline: Allie Quigley wins third 3-point shooting contest
videos.description: Allie Quigley scores a 26 in the final round to win her third 3-point contest at the WNBA All-Star game.

tracking.trackingName: WNBA One-Play (Allie Quigley wins third 3-point shooting contest) 2021/7/14 ESHEET

videos.headline: Chelsea Gray shows off moves with layup to beat buzzer
videos.description: Chelsea Gray drives inside and finishes high off the glass as the third quarter comes to an end.

videos.headline: Ogunbowale steps back for and-1 3 in win vs. Team USA
videos.description: Arike Ogunbowale makes a step-back 3-pointer in the WNBA All-Stars' 93-85 win vs. Team USA.

videos.headline: Bryant family spotted at Team USA vs. WNBA All-Star game
videos.description: Vanessa Bryant and her family check out Team USA vs. the WNBA All-Stars.

videos.headline: Arike Ogunbowale wins MVP of the WNBA All-Star game
videos.description: Arike Ogunbowale wins the 2021 WNBA All-Star Game MVP award as she scores 26 in the victory for team WNBA.

videos.headline: Ogunbowale earns MVP honors as the WNBA All-Stars beat Team USA
videos.description: The WNBA All-Stars beat Team USA 93-85 as Arike Ogunbowale wins the MVP award for her 26-point performance.
